    class SwitchRail
extends Rail

    Switch Rail on track panel

    A SwitchRail object has three ends, and a controller which determines which ends are used. If a Car moves on from the first end, the switch determines which of the other two ends it leaves from. If it moves on from one of the other two ends, it automatically leaves by the first end.
